#: ../../source/recipes/qwen3_5.rst:4
msgid "Qwen3_5ForConditionalGeneration"
msgstr "Qwen3_5ForConditionalGeneration"

#: ../../source/recipes/qwen3_5.rst:6
msgid ""
"A hybrid architecture interleaving Mamba / Gated-DeltaNet (GDN) linear-"
"attention layers with full-attention layers, shared by the **Qwen3.5 and "
"Qwen3.6** series. LMCache reinterprets the recurrent state caches as "
"opaque pages at registration time; see :doc:`../mp/hybrid_models` for the"
" general handling of Mamba / linear-attention models."
msgstr "一种混合架构，将 Mamba / Gated-DeltaNet (GDN) 线性注意力层与全注意力层交错，供 **Qwen3.5 和 Qwen3.6** 系列共享。LMCache 在注册时将递归状态缓存重新解释为不透明页面；有关 Mamba / 线性注意力模型的一般处理，请参见 :doc:`../mp/hybrid_models`。"

