#: ../../source/recipes/qwen3_5.rst:73
msgid ""
"``--mamba-cache-mode align`` is required (GDN does not support the "
"``all`` mode). ``--max-num-batched-tokens`` must be at least the unified "
"block size and below twice it — LMCache raises at engine startup "
"otherwise. ``align`` snapshots the Mamba state only at scheduler-step "
"ends, so each prefill step must advance exactly one block for every block"
" boundary to hold a reusable snapshot."
msgstr "``--mamba-cache-mode align`` 是必需的（GDN 不支持 ``all`` 模式）。``--max-num-batched-tokens`` 必须至少等于统一块大小，并且小于其两倍——否则 LMCache 在引擎启动时会引发错误。``align`` 仅在调度器步骤结束时快照 Mamba 状态，因此每个 Prefill 步骤必须精确推进一个块，以保持可重用的快照。"

